@* Documents Index Component *@
<h3>Documents Index</h3>
<p>Below is the list of materials to include in your submission:</p>
<ul class="list-group">
    <li class="list-group-item">
        <strong>1. Programming Test Submission</strong>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Full Source-Code Archive:</strong> Complete solution ZIP or GitHub link</li>
            <li>
                <strong>README.md:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Prerequisites (.NET 8/9 SDK, SQLite)</li>
                    <li>Build &amp; run instructions (migrations, API, Blazor app)</li>
                    <li>Feature walkthrough (CRUD, pagination, caching)</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Database Migration Scripts:</strong> EF Core migrations or SQL scripts</li>
            <li><strong>Unit Tests &amp; Coverage Report:</strong> Test projects and coverage summary</li>
            <li>
                <strong>API Documentation:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Swagger/OpenAPI JSON or live Swagger UI link</li>
                    <li>Postman collection export</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Dockerfile / Docker-Compose:</strong> Containerization setup</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li class="list-group-item">
        <strong>2. Technical &amp; Advocacy Extras</strong>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Architecture Diagram / Design Doc:</strong> UML or flowchart of layers</li>
            <li><strong>Performance / Caching Rationale:</strong> IMemoryCache choices and TTL</li>
            <li>
                <strong>Developer Outreach Sample (optional):</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Blog-post draft or outline (e.g., pagination deep dive)</li>
                    <li>Slide deck or outline for a 10-minute tech talk</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
